Name: "First Blood"
Text: Get the first kill in a round.

Name: "Dominating"
Text: Kill a player four times without them killing you.

Name: "Hat Trick"
Text: Capture three capture points in a single life.

Name: "The Impossible Defense"
Text: Defend a control point for an entire round without the enemy capturing it.

Name: "A Fresh Pair of Eyes"
Text: Play a full game on a map you've never played before.

Name: "Sentry Gunner"
Text: Destroy 25 enemy sentry guns.

Name: "Head of the Class"
Text: Play on a server with at least one player who has every class achievement.

Name: "Maxed Out"
Text: Reach the maximum level on an item.

Name: "Stuntman"
Text: Survive a fall of at least 30 feet.

Name: "First Do No Harm"
Text: Play as a Medic and do not kill any enemies in a round.

Name: First Blood
Text: Get the first kill in a match.

Name: Rampage!
Text: Kill five enemy heroes in a single match.

Name: Courier Hunter
Text: Kill 50 couriers in total.

Name: Denied!
Text: Deny 100 friendly creeps in total.

Name: Too Fast For You
Text: Win a match in under 20 minutes.

Name: The Art of War
Text: Win a match with at least 20 kills and no deaths.

Name: Comeback Kid
Text: Win a match after trailing by 10,000 gold.

Name: The Climb
Text: Reach level 50 on your Dota 2 profile.

Name: Free For All
Text: Win a 10 vs 10 match.

Name: Never Give Up
Text: Win a match after losing all barracks.

Name: Headshot!
Text: Kill an enemy with a headshot.

Name: The Cleaner
Text: Kill the entire enemy team in a single round.

Name: Aerial Combat
Text: Kill an airborne enemy while you are also airborne.

Name: Bomb Defusal Expert
Text: Defuse 100 bombs in total.

Name: War Bonds
Text: Earn $50,000 in total.

Name: Good Shepherd
Text: Save all hostages in a single round.

Name: The Immovable Object
Text: Defend a bombsite without any teammates getting killed.

Name: The Professional
Text: Get 500 kills with a weapon from the Professional category.

Name: King of the Kill
Text: Kill 10,000 enemies in total.

Name: Global General
Text: Reach Global General rank in Competitive mode.

Name: Two Points
Text: Hold a Combine soldier's bullet in mid-air with the Gravity Gloves.

Name: Russellsaur
Text: Discover the Russellsaur.

Name: Eye of the Geiger
Text: Kill a Headcrab using a Toilet.

Name: Good Grub
Text: Eat the Vietnamese food in the Quarantine Zone.

Name: Spice of Life
Text: Cook every type of food in the game.

Name: Payback
Text: Kill a Combine soldier with their own grenade.

Name: Gunship
Text: Defeat the Combine Gunship.

Name: Stuffed Animal Hoarder
Text: Collect all of the plushies in Russell's Secret Lab.

Name: Case Cracker
Text: Open the Combine supply crate in the Quarantine Zone.

Name: Unarmed Resistance
Text: Go through the game without killing anyone or anything.

Name: The Birth of an Assassin
Text: Be reborn as Ezio Auditore da Firenze.

Name: Welcome to the Animus 2.0
Text: Enter the Animus 2.0 for the first time.

Name: An Old Friend Returns
Text: Escape the Abstergo facility and rejoin the Assassins.

Name: Vitruvian Man
Text: Unlock all of the available upgrades for Ezio's abilities.

Name: I can see your house from here!
Text: Synchronize every Viewpoint in the game.

Name: Movin' On Up
Text: Move into a new home.

Name: That New Car Smell
Text: Buy a car.

Name: The Biggest Little Collector
Text: Collect 1,000 lifetime happiness points on a single Sim.

Name: The Jokester
Text: Tell 10 jokes to other Sims.

Name: Artisan Crafter
Text: Craft 15 unique items.

Name: "First Errand"
Text: Complete your first side quest.

Name: "A Round by the Pond"
Text: Fish up a weapon in the Flooded City.

Name: "All Pods"
Text: Fully upgrade all Pod programs.

Name: "The Minds that Emerged"
Text: Complete the game's third playthrough.

Name: "The Voice of the Forest"
Text: Meet the Forest King.

Name: "Animal Magnetism"
Text: Encounter all of the wildlife in the game.

Name: "What Are You Doing?"
Text: Discover a secret in the Amusement Park.

Name: "Lunar Tear"
Text: Obtain a Lunar Tear.

Name: "The Color of Revenge"
Text: Collect all of the revenge items.

Name: "The End of YoRHa"
Text: Complete the game's fifth playthrough.
